### Get user withdrawals (authenticated, paginated)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/withdrawals?limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get a single withdrawal (authenticated)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/withdrawals/{{withdraw_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cancel a withdrawal (authenticated)
POST {{base}}/api/v1/withdrawals/{{withdraw_id}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get withdrawal limits (authenticated)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/withdrawals/limits
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

